sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Χρήστης (CLI)
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant UI as UI Service
    participant Manager as Manager Service
    participant DDS as DDS (Database)

    User->>Auth: Request Login (Credentials)
    Auth-->>User: Επιστροφή Token
    User->>UI: Υποβολή Job (Map/Reduce files) + Token
    UI->>Auth: Επαλήθευση Token (Validate)
    Auth-->>UI: Token OK
    UI->>Manager: Προώθηση Job Details
    Manager->>DDS: Αποθήκευση νέου Job (Status: PENDING)
    DDS-->>Manager: Επιβεβαίωση (Job ID)
    Manager-->>UI: Επιστροφή Job ID
    UI-->>User: Μήνυμα Επιτυχίας & Job ID